Grinding Gears

"Equip your hero and try to survive the endless horde"

Genre: Action, RPG, hack and slash

Platform: Desktop

A lone hero is all that stands between his village and the unending horde that threatens it

8-bit graphics with retro adventure music and sound effects

Mechanics: The player will fight through rounds with ever increasing difficulty which will require them to properly equip their avatar with gear from the village
which can be accessed in between set rounds
Controls: Mouse and keyboard, primary WASD and the Q & E keys

